":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:22:02.000Z","msg":"我真係唔明，明明我自己所有識嘅都唔贊成分區，但次次都有人吹分區，然後好多人贊成<br />\n仲有，每次分區俾狗咬走好多手足之後，夜晚上下連登睇下，吖屌，又有好多post話好成功架喎"},{"pid":"f058ecd3ba6255286da920aa1c9b4fd8ec8f9d74","tid":1652480,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:25:15.000Z","msg":"活動貴精不貴多，要多啲時間宣傳，benefit要大過cost <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c12d899e2671ad94bcb5ec9c756be326ed84fb3","tid":1652480,"uid":76224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T19:40:59.000Z","msg":"見到隔離post又再推分區，鼓勵繼續分區搞，我唔知講咩好喇唉"},{"pid":"76976d7eb03d488372a32c5559f83c7bea94e01a","tid":1652480,"uid":50290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:47:18.000Z","msg":"好矛盾, 其實主要係無大台<br />\n太多分支, 行動唔統一<br />\n但呢場運動標榜既就係無大台<br />\n其實簡單 d 講好似遊行咁<br />\n民陣吹雞同連登tg吹雞既分別<br />\n大家都好清楚<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 就算點都要繼續撐住<br />\n不分不割不篤<br />\n因為我地係香港人"},{"pid":"51e6a56b801f7e4a26e0e5251f2380449ec68e42","tid":1652480,"uid":98993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:48:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29e1959b0737a9f4fa310a8a29e520de0cf22012","tid":1652480,"uid":76224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:12:47.000Z","msg":"要分真係最多分兩區，我地根本就唔夠人，唔係一句少人可以玩快閃就得，依家係狗多過自己人好撚多，一出黎就俾佢地收左皮"},{"pid":"9671b4f8b85a66def0cba1a3013ac3428f8b3bc6","tid":1652480,"uid":76224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:03:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b825a2f95360e3a2aee98ba790921ec1a03d1c62","tid":1652480,"uid":221463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:04:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e2234b8c3fae86c8cca90957d13b7a3749dbc63b","tid":1652480,"uid":221463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:06:10.000Z","msg":"真係覺得遍地開花效果一般<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ebdec2a325ff4cb6fc204ace9f3c6146de969e","tid":1652480,"uid":76224,"li